This is just a wrapper around opengl.
Files are automatically generated from opengl header files using c2ffi.
Some types may still be incorrect and you have to cast them yourself to use specific functions.
OpenGL typedefs are not included in file, and just replaced by it's definitions.

Compile all libs:
make

Genereate dale files only
make <filename>.dt

Run test progam:
make test

